Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.games.states

Interface GameState

All Known Implementing Classes:
ActivateProductionState, BuyCardState, EndTurnState, FirstActionState, TakeMarbleState, WhiteConversionCardState
public interface GameState
GameState is the generic interface for game state. All methods could be override by different game state classes.
